001package org.biopax.paxtools.impl.level3;
002
003import org.biopax.paxtools.model.BioPAXElement;
004import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.PhysicalEntity;
005import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.Stoichiometry;
006
007
008public class StoichiometryImpl extends L3ElementImpl implements Stoichiometry
009{
010        private float stoichiometricCoefficient = UNKNOWN_FLOAT;
011        private PhysicalEntity physicalEntity;
012
013
014        public StoichiometryImpl() {}
015
016        public Class<? extends Stoichiometry> getModelInterface()
017        {
018                return Stoichiometry.class;
019        }
020
021        @Override
022        protected boolean semanticallyEquivalent(BioPAXElement element)
023        {
024
025                boolean value = false;
026                if (element instanceof Stoichiometry)
027                {
028                        Stoichiometry that = (Stoichiometry) element;
029                        if (that.getPhysicalEntity() != null && this.getPhysicalEntity() != null)
030                        {
031                                value = (that.getStoichiometricCoefficient() ==
032                                         this.getStoichiometricCoefficient()) &&
033                                        that.getPhysicalEntity().equals(this.getPhysicalEntity());
034
035                        }
036                }
037                return value;
038        }
039
040        @Override
041        public int equivalenceCode()
042        {
043                return ((int) this.getStoichiometricCoefficient()) +
044               ((this.getPhysicalEntity() != null)
045                ? 31 * this.getPhysicalEntity().hashCode()
046                : 0);
047        }
048
049        public PhysicalEntity getPhysicalEntity()
050        {
051                return physicalEntity;
052        }
053
054        public void setPhysicalEntity(PhysicalEntity PhysicalEntity)
055        {
056                this.physicalEntity = PhysicalEntity;
057        }
058
059        
060        public float getStoichiometricCoefficient()
061        {
062                return stoichiometricCoefficient;
063        }
064
065        public void setStoichiometricCoefficient(float newStoichiometricCoefficient)
066        {
067                stoichiometricCoefficient = newStoichiometricCoefficient;
068        }
069}
